*Prošlog* meseca smo bili na putovanju. (We were travelling last month.)

*Prošlog* leta smo se udali. (We got married last year.)

Prijatelji su nas pozvali da im se pridružimo u *prošlog* vikendu. (Our friends invited us to join them last weekend.)

*Prošlom* nedeljom smo bili na proslavi. (We were celebrating last Sunday.)

Izabrali smo najbolji film u *prošloj* godini. (We chose the best movie of the last year.)